# TNA Form 02 layout (approved)

## Scope

- **Print only** — on-screen preview in `TnaForm02Preview.tsx` stays modern/summary layout.
- Official output via `TnaForm02Document` rendered at print time (`printTnaForm02Pdf`).

## Document title

`DOST TNA FORM 02 - TECHNOLOGY NEEDS ASSESSMENT REPORT`

## Pagination

- Physical page footers via CSS `@page @bottom-center` with `counter(page)` / `counter(pages)` — matches actual printed sheet count.
- No per-section inline footers (avoid misleading "Page X of 6" when content fits fewer sheets).
- `FormBlock` + `break-inside: avoid` — section titles stay with content.

## Print path

- In-page `window.print()` via `#tna-form-02-print-root` + `body.tna-form-02-printing`.
- `createRoot` render (do not clone preview; do not use popup `document.write`).
- Hide portal metadata in print: no Document Ref, Application ID, AI/draft badges.

## Key files

- `src/app/components/tnaForm02/TnaForm02Document.tsx`
- `src/app/utils/tnaForm02Print.tsx`
- `src/styles/tnaForm02.css`
- `src/app/constants/tnaForm02Layout.ts`
